  "cscw_dialogue": [
    {
      "turn_id": 1,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "我们需要画一个序列图，展示用户怎么通过我们的GitHub App完成认证和任务。整体流程是：用户打开前端，然后需要先后完成Azure AD和GitHub的双重登录，最后才能操作任务。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "User",
        "GhApp",
        "AzureAD",
        "GitHub"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白了。所以GhApp是我们应用的前端部分对吧？用户先打开它，然后App主动请求认证？这两个交互是同步的还是异步的？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "User",
        "GhApp"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "对，GhApp就是前端。用户打开页面后，App会立即弹出认证提示。这两个都是普通的消息交互，不用激活生命线。接下来关键的一步是用户必须登录Azure AD，这里要用实线加号表示激活。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "User",
        "AzureAD"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，我先把开头画出来：用户打开前端，App请求认证，然后用户激活Azure AD的登录流程。Azure AD验证完成后，需要把结果返回给GhApp对吧？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "User",
        "GhApp",
        "AzureAD"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "没错，Azure AD返回的时候要带上user.email，而且要用虚线表示这是异步回调。但这还没完，用户还得再登录一次GitHub，同样是激活生命线的形式。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "AzureAD",
        "GhApp",
        "User",
        "GitHub"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "所以GitHub登录也是必须的？不是二选一？另外GitHub确认登录后返回给GhApp，这个回调需要带什么信息吗，比如用户组权限？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "User",
        "GitHub",
        "GhApp"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 7,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "两个都要登，是顺序执行的。GitHub回调只需要确认登录成功就行，具体的用户组权限是在最后一步才判断——用户完成任务时，系统会根据他能访问的groups来决定展示哪些tasks。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "GitHub",
        "GhApp",
        "User"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 8,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "画好了。最后一步是用户回到GhApp，可以操作任务，这里我用普通消息线，备注上基于用户可访问的groups来完成tasks。整个流程：开前端→Azure AD登录→GitHub登录→任务操作，对吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "User",
        "GhApp"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 9,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "repair",
      "utterance": "等等，最后一步的描述有点问题。应该是\"User can complete tasks, based on groups the user has access to\"，你写的是\"基于用户组权限操作\"，意思对但不够准确，而且我注意到你漏了\"the user has access to\"这个关键限定。另外确认一下，Azure AD返回的那条虚线，你标注了user.email provided吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "User",
        "GhApp",
        "AzureAD"
      ],
      "is_repair": true
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 10,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "repair",
      "utterance": "抱歉，我修正一下：AzureAD到GhApp的虚线回调明确标注\"AzureAD login confirmed, user.email provided\"；最后一步改为\"User can complete tasks, based on groups the user has access to\"。这样描述就精确了。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "AzureAD",
        "GhApp",
        "User"
      ],
      "is_repair": true
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 11,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "完美，现在整个认证流程清晰多了。双重登录保障安全，最后根据用户权限动态展示任务，这就是我们想要表达的完整逻辑。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "User",
        "GhApp",
        "AzureAD",
        "GitHub"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    }
  ],
